==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Wikiup
<hw>Wik"i*up`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Of North American
Indian origin; cf. Dakota <ets>wakeya</ets>, <ets>wokeya</ets>.]</ety>
<def>The hut used by the nomadic Indian tribes of the arid regions of
the west and southwest United States, typically elliptical in form, with
a rough frame covered with reed mats or grass or brushwood.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Wikke</ent>⟦br⟧
